query: income statement for the last 3 fiscal years
expanded_query: Income statement OR consolidated statements of income OR statements of operations for the last three fiscal years OR three most recent fiscal years OR annual periods ended OR fiscal year ended, including quarterly reports such as statements for the quarter ended. Also include synonyms like profit and loss statement, statement of earnings, and results of operations to improve retrieval from SEC filings.
